<author>Mark 439</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Puipa, huihpi a hung nung hi,
 Tui kinawk chuh a sang hi!
 Van la a hah nim mah mah mai in,
 Belh ding, panpih ding umlo;
 Ka manthai diu khawk salo maw
 Bang di'n Na ip thei em
 Mitphetkal chenga a hung hat zinga
 Thihna a hung naih lai hi'n

[V2]
 &quot;Huih leh tui kinawk ka thu'n a nung ui,
 Hai kei un!
 Huihpi mutin tui kinawk mahleh,
 Dawi leh kau, mi leh sa bang cheng hung mahleh;
 Kuong chuh tui a chun tum thei diek puona,
 Tuipi, lei leh van Lal a um ziekin;
 Ziehaw hin Ka thu a awi chiet ui,
 Hai kei un! Hai kei un!
 Ziehaw hin Ka thu a awi chiet ui,
 Hai! hai kei un!&quot;

[V3]
 2. Puipa, lungthim a lungkham in,
 Tuni'n lungdawng in ka khun;
 Ka lunggil lungkhamna a lien ie,
 Tho inla, ei hukdam in;
 Gitlohna tuihat leh thawkna'n,
 Ka thagau a suol hi;'
 Mang ding ka hi! mang ding ka hi! Puipa,
 Kin inla hung hih thipin.

[V4]
 3. Puipa, lauhum chuh abei tai,
 Chawlhna nuom ahung kipan;
 Nisa'n tui tawilo chung chuh a salh,
 Ka lungthim a kipak hi;
 Um zingin aw Tanpa deihum,
 Kei ngawn ei nusie ki'n;
 Kipakin, kuongchawlhna nuom tak siem ka,
 Nuom takin zie chun chawl ka.</lyrics>
<title>PEACE BE STILL</title>
</song>